  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/466347d3ef9481590c64506c8bafdaeb.poster.avif?t=1747834878\" width=768 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/466347d3ef9481590c64506c8bafdaeb.webm?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/466347d3ef9481590c64506c8bafdaeb.mp4?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first-person psychological horror game, survival is key. You are tasked with surviving as long as possible. You will feel how terrible it is to live in a white room. The game's core mechanic revolves around avoiding dangerous hallucinations and terrifying creatures that appear in various unique environments.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Horror</strong>: White Room: Mind's Prison focuses on psychological horror, creating an intense atmosphere where paranoia, fear, and survival instincts are your only tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/788f268210a3b5c189a421ef25c052a1.poster.avif?t=1747834878\" width=768 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/788f268210a3b5c189a421ef25c052a1.webm?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/788f268210a3b5c189a421ef25c052a1.mp4?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Progression</strong>: As you survive each level, the day counter in the White Room increases, indicating your passage of time within the prison. Every new day brings new dangers and more complex challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive the Hallucinations</strong>: Each level presents new, surreal locations that challenge your mind. Every environment offers its own set of dangers.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person psychological horror with immersive environments</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique and unsettling environments that challenge your mind and senses</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric sound design and visuals to enhance the horror experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you overcome your fears and survive in the White Room, or will your mind ultimately betray you? The choice is yours.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/466347d3ef9481590c64506c8bafdaeb.poster.avif?t=1747834878\" width=768 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/466347d3ef9481590c64506c8bafdaeb.webm?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/466347d3ef9481590c64506c8bafdaeb.mp4?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first-person psychological horror game, survival is key. You are tasked with surviving as long as possible. You will feel how terrible it is to live in a white room. The game's core mechanic revolves around avoiding dangerous hallucinations and terrifying creatures that appear in various unique environments.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Horror</strong>: White Room: Mind's Prison focuses on psychological horror, creating an intense atmosphere where paranoia, fear, and survival instincts are your only tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/788f268210a3b5c189a421ef25c052a1.poster.avif?t=1747834878\" width=768 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/788f268210a3b5c189a421ef25c052a1.webm?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3370260/extras/788f268210a3b5c189a421ef25c052a1.mp4?t=1747834878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Progression</strong>: As you survive each level, the day counter in the White Room increases, indicating your passage of time within the prison. Every new day brings new dangers and more complex challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive the Hallucinations</strong>: Each level presents new, surreal locations that challenge your mind. Every environment offers its own set of dangers.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person psychological horror with immersive environments</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique and unsettling environments that challenge your mind and senses</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric sound design and visuals to enhance the horror experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you overcome your fears and survive in the White Room, or will your mind ultimately betray you? The choice is yours.</p>",
